data.description: This gorgeous home is located in the well-established Millers Creek Community. This beautiful and spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath home boasts over 2200 sq/ft on half an acre. This home features the owner’s suite on the first floor, stainless steel appliances, updated LVP flooring in the kitchen, huge fenced in backyard, tons of storage throughout the home, and a covered patio in the backyard. The location of this home is perfect with close proximity to shopping, entertainment, dining options, and easy access to I-20. Don’t miss this one!
